description: Rush is a 20 year old engineering student who is also heavily involved in sports.His favorite outdoor activity is snowboarding and on the day that we met up with him for his Next Door Male shoot, he had just come in off the slopes. He was tired and definitely ready to take a load off. Watch Rush as he unwinds and enjoys some personal time by himself. The last scene includes an intense final moment in the bathroom -- we're just glad we didn't get any complaints from the neighbor on the other side of the wall.Enjoy.
title: Rush
